# =============================================================================
# Ship bathymetry repo - root .gitignore
#
# Repo total: ~382 GB on disk. Tracked content target: < 50 MB.
# Heavy data is either re-downloadable or regenerable; do not commit it.
# =============================================================================

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Heavy data dirs (raw inputs, derived outputs, source archives)
# Note: list dataset archive dirs explicitly so we don't shadow
# .trellis/tasks/archive/ which IS tracked (Trellis archived tasks).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/raw/
**/derived/
/archive/
# JAMSTEC tree (unified 2026-05-16 by task 05-11-singlebeam-integration PR-A;
# the heavy zip / 7z payloads are also caught by the binary-extension block
# below, but explicit dir entries keep `git status` predictable):
jamstec/multibeam/archive/
jamstec/archive/
jamstec/gravity_data/
# NCEI tree (renamed from NCEI_singlebeam/ 2026-05-16 in PR-B; PR-C
# 2026-05-16 populated tracklines_{nc,xyz}/ + archive/ subdirs).
# tracklines_nc/*.nc and tracklines_xyz/*.xyz are caught by the global
# extension globs below. The .txt rules are scoped tightly to avoid
# shadowing tracked .txt files elsewhere (jamstec/multibeam/docs/*.txt):
# - tracklines_nc/*.txt = 2 upstream sidecars (NCEI_Ara1.txt,
#   validation_results.txt) totaling ~18 MB.
# - archive/zhoushuai_processed_M/*.txt = 3 quadrant .txt files from M.rar
#   totaling ~4 GB.
# archive/ contents are caught file-by-file (not as a directory) so
# provenance sidecars (SOURCE.md, README.md) under each archive subdir
# remain trackable. The big-extension globs (*.zip, *.rar, *.xyz, etc.)
# below catch the heavy payloads.
ncei/tracklines_nc/*.txt
ncei/archive/zhoushuai_processed_M/*.txt

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Generic binary / data formats - never commit
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.parquet
*.zip
*.rar
*.7z
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.nc
*.xyz
*.npz
*.npy
*.pkl
*.pickle
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.feather

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Logs and runtime artifacts
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/output/logs/
*.log
*.nohup.log
*.pid
*.tmp

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Python
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Editor / OS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Trained model artifacts (Step 11 baselines)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/baselines_*/
*.joblib
*.bin
*.model
*.lgbm
*.xgb
